 safe assets such as low-risk fixed-income instruments by relaxing the leverage-ratio rule and increasing risk-based capital requirements.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aBank capital. 0aBank liquidity. 0aCapital market. 0aFinance. 4aCross Currency-Basis. 4aGlobal Finanzkrise. 4aKreditbewertungsanpassung. 4aOTC-Markt. 4aVerschuldungs"e. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Insurance / General.2bisacsh  aAll-to-all trade.  aCentral clearing.  aCross-currency basis.  aFunding value adjustment.  aGlobal Financial Crisis.  aOTC markets.  aSupplementary leverage ratio.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCz978311065906108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2022 Englishz978311099282308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2022z9783110992922oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831106731280 cprintz978311067302940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067305040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110673050423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110673050/original  a978-3-11-065906-1  De Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCb2020  a978-3-11-076682-0  DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  a978-3-11-099282-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL